text: Brandon White (born 13 January 1997) is an Australian rules footballer playing for the St Kilda Football Club in the Australian Football League (AFL). He was drafted by St Kilda with their second selection and fortieth overall in the 2015 national draft. He made his debut in the fifty-eight point win against the in round 23, 2016 at Etihad Stadium.
